This repository contains an addon **Throwable C4** for **ArmA 3** game. You can feel free to use, modify and reupload this mod, it created just for fun.

This mod adds ะก4, which can be attached to any surface, including vehicles. 
Works as a grenade, can be exploded by Shift+C hotkey. Hotkey can be changed in CBA key settings.
